title: Chinese noodles with vegetables and minced beef
ingredients: ['1 packet Chinese egg noodles', '3 tablespoons vegetable oil', '1 onion, chopped', '250g minced beef', '150g soya beans (edamame)', '150g any vegetables - grated carrot, minced leek, salad onion, green beans', '1/2 teaspoon Chinese 5 spice powder', '1/2 teaspoon ground ginger', '1 tablespoon fish sauce', '100ml soy sauce']
